snippet.title: Mana Khemia: Alchemists of Al-Revis (PS2) - No Commentary #1 | Gameplay Archive
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage of Mana Khemia: Alchemists of Al-Revis, the ninth installment in Gust's Atelier series of RPGs for PlayStation 2. Starting from the very beginning of the game up until the third week of the first chapter. Recorded on original hardware.

--

The MoeGamer Gameplay Archive includes commentary-free, correct aspect ratio videos of a variety of games, new and old, recorded on original hardware where possible.

You are welcome to use this footage in your own projects; however, a link back to this channel and/or MoeGamer.net would be appreciated if you do. Thank you!
